{"id":"SANLI09","scripts":[{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"三笠大先輩、昨日の宴会はどうもありがとうございました。…でも大先輩が言ってたこと、私にはまだちょっとよく分からなくて……","side":2,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","actor":307060,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","say":"なら、我と一回演習で勝負でもしてみるか？","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"actor":305110,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"三笠大先輩と…ですか？","side":0,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","actor":307060,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"うむ。切磋琢磨は重要だ。何かがひらめくかも知れぬぞ。","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"はい！全力で行かせていただきます！演習海域はちょうど空いていますから、三笠大先輩、今から行きましょう！","side":0,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","actor":307060,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"我はここでも構わぬが……まあ良い。では演習海域に出航しよう。って瑞鶴、ちょっと待てーー","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"（あの時、ダンスは苦手だと言ったのに、我の足を一回も踏まなかったな……）","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"flashin":{"alpha":[1,0],"delay":1,"black":true,"dur":1},"flashout":{"alpha":[0,1],"black":true,"dur":1},"say":"一刻後","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"瑞鶴！セイレーンとの戦いでの勢いはどうした！","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"攻撃が全てわざとらしすぎる！どこを狙っているかひと目でわかるぞ！","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"やっぱり、大先輩には勝てない……か……","side":0,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","actor":307060,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"そんなことあるか！今のはお主の全力ではあるまい！","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"……兵装には問題ないはず、でもなぜ……大先輩相手にはやっぱり……","side":0,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","actor":307060,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"まだ気づいておらぬか。お主は我と戦う時、そしてセイレーン・エンタープライズと戦う時と比べて決定的な差があるーー","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"……？","side":0,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","actor":307060,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"我を傷つけるのを恐れるあまり、全ての攻撃前に躊躇しているのだ。","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"…戦いを単純に考えすぎる者もいるが、お主はその逆だ。戦闘に入ったら、余計なことを考えるな！","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"そう言われても……！","side":0,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","actor":307060,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"お主が気にすることもわかる。しかしだ、お主が自分の道を決めない限り、誰もがそれを決められまい。","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"我の後を追っかけるのも構わぬ。だが――「全てを賭ける」と決めているのなら、最後まで貫け！","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"私の、全て……わかりました。三笠大先輩！またいつかお手合わせお願いできませんか？","side":0,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","actor":307060,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"構わぬぞ。お主のためなら、我はその第一歩となろう。","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"…ただ、あまり長く待たせるでないぞ。その後はお主の努力が必要になるのだからな――","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"flashin":{"alpha":[1,0],"delay":1,"black":true,"dur":1},"blackBg":true,"side":1,"dir":-1,"flashout":{"alpha":[0,1],"black":true,"dur":1},"say":"……","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"flashin":{"alpha":[1,0],"delay":1,"black":true,"dur":1},"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","say":"ふぅ……ここだな。","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"flashout":{"alpha":[0,1],"black":true,"dur":1},"actor":305110,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"この旗は、一体……？","side":0,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:95}","actor":307050,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"かつて我を勝利に導いた旗だ。","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"この旗さえあれば、お主らはきっと勝利への道を見つけ出せる。","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"威厳で敵勢を挫き、勇気で性能差を補い、信念と根性で最後の最後まで粘り勝つ。","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"かの時代でもここでも「奇跡」は起こりえぬ。だが「奇跡的な勝利」は確かにあるのだ。この旗は、我が信念とともに、お主に預けるとしよう！","side":1,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","actor":305110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"}],"fadeOut":1.5,"fadeType":1,"fadein":1.5,"mode":2}